reviewText: Quick and straight to the point. Some useful functionalities learned. In terms of learning motivation, it would benefit from a better design example to work on.

I have been working on Canva for more than a year and I wanted to see how to create a mind map using the same. I liked the video as it informed me about the important elements needed to build a basic mind map but the aesthetics of it weren't up to the mark. I understand this was a tutorial, but the teacher could have aimed for something more visually pleasing. Thank you
stacey,you are awesome and gave exact information required.
I already use Canva on daily basis, and I got to learn a lot of different tools.

To my mind this short course is worth your attention, because new software and approach in learning process allow you to learn a new skill during a short period of time and make the result by your own hands.As for me, the main disadvantage of this course is the fact, that cloud inerface of "Canva" programm is too tiny and it is painfull for eyes to work with it. Also currently it is uncomfortable a lot of. I hope that these problems will be solved in the nearest future by the team of "Coursera"!
A fresh introduction to a mind-mapping tool and more.
I enjoyed learning how to make interactive mind maps after many years of making paper arty crafty ones, these can be filed and shared and adapted for presentations.
The course is amazing, I'm so lucky to know this course
Very informative and colorful! :) I enjoyed taking this course.
Interesting, easy to follow the instructor and a great tool, especially for people who work in education.
Es buenisimo y muy util, es una nueva herramienta que podemos ocupar cuando ocupemos recopilar informacion y presentar
Great course! I've been using Canva for quite some time now and the course added some tips that I can use.
Easy to follow and very practical
This course is very useful. creating mind map using canva is much easier and helpful than a written form of mind map.
It was an excellent guided project.
This guided project is cool, I never explore this yet before, thanks for this guided project. Thanks too to Stacey :)
It was amazing learning the Canva mind map with Stacey. Very interactive and great session conducted.However, I struggled a little bit to use the Workspace as it was quite slow for me.
It is a very concise and precise course for canva beginners
Enjoyed it and learned some new things that gave me some great ideas for presenting content to my students.
Easy to follow yet very useful course. I learned a lot in a short period of time.
Canva is a great way to create a mind map and this course quickly and easily showed me how.
Learnt design in a very simple way and would like to explore more of the same.
An hour spent well learning this!
It was good course, I love it because you can learn many skills and ideas for your school projects or marketing projects
Its very easy way to learn
Nice project to improve my presentation skill

reviewText: I appreciate the initiative taken by Coursera to create a platform where individuals can learn in an interactive manner. The step by step guidances really makes an individual remember the protocols for the process he/she wants to learn. However, the 'rhyme' servers is a little bit slow, maybe due to the heavy usage and the display screen for the learner is quite small.
An excellent tool for making your presentations more lively and interactive.
this is a very helpful course.
